Install docker + docker-compose 


ideally install pre-requisites seperately in ~/bin/xqa/
apache-maven-3.5.3-bin.tar.gz
node-v8.11.1-linux-x64.tar.xz
jdk-8u171-linux-x64.tar.gz
and use them to build

git clone https://github.com/jameshnsears/xqa-perf

cd xqa-perf/bin
./build.sh
docker images

--

docker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml -p "dev" up -d --scale xqa-shard=20

